				functionalModemProtocolHms(2),
				functionalModemProtocolDocsis(3),
				functionalModemProtocolRis(4)
				}
			ACCESS read-write
			STATUS mandatory
			DESCRIPTION
				"Modem protocol in use.
				Writing this object resets the unit and changes the protocol
				and may thus cause loss of remote connection.
				All communication settings should be reviewed carefully
				before writing this object.
				1 = CATVisor (Teleste proprietary 'TSEMP') protocol
				2 = HMS protocol
				3 = DOCSIS"
			::= { commonModemStatus 8 }

		
